gw.plugin.document.impl

Class BaseDocumentProductionImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.plugin.document.impl.BaseDocumentProductionImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, IDocumentProductionBase, java.rmi.Remote
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseGosuDocumentProductionImpl, BaseMailMergeDocumentProductionImpl, BaseServerSideDocumentProductionImpl

    public abstract class BaseDocumentProductionImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDocumentProductionBase
    The root implementation of the internal IDocumentProduction implementations. All of the document creation classes which are part of the core Guidewire code extend from this class. They generally only support synchronous creation of documents.

    see IDocumentProductionBase for more information.

    Author:
    bjohnson
